<p>
<seg id=1> Recently liberated Western tourists in Yemen said that when Yemeni government forces fired on their kidnappers in an attempt to free them the kidnappers used them as human shields. </seg>
<seg id=2> Four tourists were killed during Tuesday's firefight, and twelve were saved after the crisis. </seg>
<seg id=3> The Yemeni government said that Yemeni forces fired on the kidnappers when they were clearly in a potentially fatal situation. </seg>
<seg id=4> However, some of the rescued tourists said that shots were fired only after the Yemeni forces began their rescue action. </seg>
</p>
